Christine Delaroche https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Christine_Delaroche 0 Christine Delaroche (born 24 May 1944) is a French actress and singer. She has appeared in 21 films and television shows since 1965. She starred in the 1966 film Un monde nouveau, which was directed by Vittorio De Sica.
